{
  "texts": [
    "The discussion in Sects.",
    "3.1-3.3 is focused on the on-training integration of TDA.",
    "That is, building topological neural architectures.",
    "However, a holistic view should also consider TDA's contribution to post-training (deep topological analytics).",
    "These analytics use TDA to study the 'shape' of a trained model."
  ]
}